      <abstract>
        <p>The author was in Płaszów camp and August 6, 1944 she was taken to Auschwitz. Living
          conditions in the camp, selections. Transport to Bergen-Belsen (October 31, 1944), then to
          Aschersleben. Liberation by American forces during evacuation towards Dachau (April 15,
          1945)</p>
